(56, 27, 'Content', '    <h1 class=\"font-inter-bold text-primary fs-20\">Madagascar Car Rental: Explore with Ease</h1>\r\n                <h2 class=\"font-inter-regular fs-14\">Explore Affordable Madagascar Car Rental Options</h2>\r\n <hr>\r\n               <p>If you want to organize your itinerary on the way, it\'s possible to rent a car at Madagascar Green Tours. Car rental is available for a minimum of 6 days. Our cars are always driven by one of our drivers. Our drivers speak Malagasy, English and French<br><span class=\"fontRegular\" style=\"scrollbar-color: rgb(241, 241, 244) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">We have the following cars for rent:</span></p><table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"--bs-table-color: #071437; --bs-table-bg: transparent; --bs-table-border-color: #F1F1F4; --bs-table-accent-bg: transparent; --bs-table-striped-color: #071437; --bs-table-striped-bg: rgba(249,249,249, 0.75); --bs-table-active-color: #071437; --bs-table-active-bg: #F9F9F9; --bs-table-hover-color: #071437; --bs-table-hover-bg: #F9F9F9; width: 429.75px; border-color: rgb(241, 241, 244);\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"color: rgb(7, 20, 55); box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 9999px inset;\">Place</td><td style=\"color: rgb(7, 20, 55); box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 9999px inset;\">Price</td></tr><tr><td style=\"color: rgb(7, 20, 55); box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 9999px inset;\">up to 3 persons</td><td style=\"color: rgb(7, 20, 55); box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 9999px inset;\">40 Euro per day</td></tr><tr><td style=\"color: rgb(7, 20, 55); box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 9999px inset;\">up to 4 persons</td><td style=\"color: rgb(7, 20, 55); box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 9999px inset;\">70 Euro per day</td></tr><tr><td style=\"color: rgb(7, 20, 55); box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 9999px inset;\">up to 6 persons</td><td style=\"color: rgb(7, 20, 55); box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 9999px inset;\">58 Euro per day