(66, 32, 'Content', '<h1 class=\"font-inter-bold text-primary text-center\">About Us</h1>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal;mso-outline-level:2\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Welcome to </span><b style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Madagascar\r\nGreen Tours</b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">, your gateway to discovering the true heart of Madagascar. As\r\nthe </span><b style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">best Madagascar tour operator</b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">, we are deeply passionate about\r\ncrafting personalised travel experiences that showcase the island’s unique\r\nnature, vibrant culture, and warm hospitality. Whether you are a wildlife\r\nenthusiast, a beach lover, a bird-watcher, or an adventurer, our tour company\r\nprovides an authentic and unforgettable journey.</span></p><div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:fr\"=\"\">\r\n\r\n<hr size=\"2\" width=\"100%\" align=\"center\">\r\n\r\n</span></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal;mso-outline-level:3\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-fareast-language:fr\"=\"\">Who We Are<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:fr\"=\"\">For over <b>25\r\nyears</b>, Madagascar Green Tours has operated as a premier <b>tour company</b>\r\nbased in Antananarivo, employing local experts who know every corner of this\r\nextraordinary island. Our team includes passionate </span><a href=\"https://madagascar-green-tours.com/madagascar-tour-guide\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:fr\"=\"\">Madagascar tour guides</span></b></a><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:fr\"=\"\"> fluent in English, French, and many\r\nregional languages. They share not only the sights, but stories—of endemic\r\nspecies, remote communities, lush rainforests, and sweeping coastal landscapes.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:fr\"=\"\">As a\r\nmulti-award-winning tour operator, we focus on:<o:p></o:p></span></p><ul type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:fr\"=\"\">Tailor-made travel itineraries\r\n     that adapt to your preferences, interests, and budget<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:fr\"=\"\">Small group and private tours\r\n     to ensure authenticity and personal attention<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-ma