(86, 39, 'Content', '<section id=\"about\" class=\"container content-section bg-light\" aria-labelledby=\"about-heading\">\r\n  <div class=\"card-styled\">\r\n    <div class=\"card-styled-body\">\r\n      <img src=\"/uploads/media/images/hotel-ranomafana.jpg\" class=\"float-image desktop-img\" alt=\"Ring-tailed lemur in Madagascar rainforest\" decoding=\"async\">\r\n        \r\n        <h1 class=\"text-center text-primary font-inter-extra-bold fs-20\">\r\n          Madagascar Travel Information – Hotels, Camping &amp; Tours        </h1>\r\n      <h3 class=\"text-center font-inter-bold text-secondary fs-14\">\r\n        Accommodations in Madagascar – Hotels, Bungalows &amp; Lodges      </h3>\r\n      <img src=\"/uploads/media/images/hotel-ranomafana.jpg\" class=\"float-image mobile-img\" alt=\"Ring-tailed lemur in Madagascar rainforest\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\">\r\n      <p>When planning your Madagascar tour, one of the most important questions is where you will stay. Tourism in Madagascar is still developing, so European-style five-star hotels are rare outside major tourist hubs. In the capital city Antananarivo, and in popular destinations such as Nosy Be or Sainte Marie, visitors will find a selection of comfortable hotels and beach resorts. However, in many other towns, accommodations are simpler and more traditional.</p>\r\n<p>At Madagascar Green Tours, we carefully select hotels, lodges, and bungalows based on 20+ years of local experience. Since Madagascar does not have an official hotel rating system, we evaluate properties ourselves, focusing on cleanliness, comfort, quality of meals, and guest service. Most accommodations are charming mid-range hotels run by Malagasy owners, often built in harmony with nature and respectful of local communities.</p>\r\n<p>In more remote areas, travelers should be prepared for basic rooms with limited amenities, as luxury properties are rare outside the main tourist areas. If you prefer to stay exclusively in upscale lodges or boutique hotels, please let us know in advance. The few luxury resorts in Madagascar are in high demand and tend to book out quickly.\r\n</p>      <img src=\"/uploads/media/images/shape-6.webp\" alt=\"shape-6\" style=\"position: absolute; bottom: 0; right: 0;\">\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section>\r\n  <div class=\"top_inside_divider\"></div>\r\n  <img src=\"/uploads/media/images/hotel-ranomafana-large.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; margin-top: -32px\" alt=\"shape-6\">\r\n\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"container mb-4\" style=\"margin-top: -90px\">\r\n  <div class=\"card-styled\">\r\n    <div class=\"card-styled-body px-4\">\r\n      <h3 class=\"text-center font-inter-extra-bold text-primary\">\r\n         Camping in Madagascar - A Unique Adventure Close to Nature      </h3>\r\n      <p>Because we specialize in tours “off the beaten path,” some itineraries include camping experiences. \r\n                        This is the best way to immerse yourself in Madagascar\'s pristine nature, \r\n                        far from crowded tourist areas. We provide modern lightweight tents with excellent \r\n                        waterproof protection (up to 4000 mm water column), ensuring comfort even during tropical rains.</p>\r\n      <p>Guests usually sleep in single or double tents, with extra space for luggage and equipment. \r\n                        While camping, our professional cooks prepare three fresh meals daily, with special attention \r\n                        to vegetarian diets and allergy-friendly options. Many travelers say the food served on our \r\n                        camping tours is among the best they enjoy during their entire trip. It\'s a truly memorable \r\n                        way to experience Madagascar\'s landscapes and wilderness.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"container content-section bg-light\">\r\n  <div class=\"card-styled\">\r\n    <div class=\"card-styled-body\">\r\n      <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-lg-5 col-md-12 col-sm-12\">\r\n          <img src=\"/uploads/media/images/huyndai-h1.webp\" alt=\"car\" style=\"width:100%; border-radius: 10px\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"col-lg-7 col-md-12 col-sm-12\">\r\n          <h4 class=\"text-primary text-left font-inter-extra-bold fs-16\">\r\n          Vehicles - Safe &amp; Reliable Transport Across Madagascar</h4>\r\n          <p class=\"text text-justify\">\r\n            Traveling across Madagascar requires reliable transport, as distances are long and road conditions \r\n                            can be challenging. Our vehicles for Madagascar tours include 4x4 off-road cars, minibuses, \r\n                            and larger buses, depending on group size. Each vehicle meets strict safety standards, \r\n                            is fully insured, and is driven by experienced Malagasy drivers.          </p>\r\n          <p>\r\n          Traveling across Madagascar requires reliable transport, as distances are long and road conditions \r\n                            can be challenging. Our vehicles for Madagascar tours include 4x4 off-road cars, minibuses, \r\n                            and larger buses, depending on group size. Each vehicle meets strict safety standards, \r\n                            is fully insured, and is driven by experienced Malagasy drivers.          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"container content-section bg-light mb-4\">\r\n  <div class=\"card-styled\">\r\n    <div class=\"card-styled-body\">\r\n      <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12\">\r\n          <h4 class=\"text-primary text-left font-inter-extra-bold fs-16\">\r\n          Travel Security - Your Safety Comes First</h4>\r\n          <p class=\"text text-justify\">\r\n          When booking a trip, safety and financial protection are essential. \r\n                            Every package tour we offer includes a travel security note, required by European and Swiss law. \r\n                            This guarantees that your prepaid travel expenses are insured in the unlikely event of insolvency \r\n                            by the tour operator.          </p>\r\n          <p>\r\n          If you encounter travel offers without such a security guarantee, proceed with caution. \r\n                            Reliable tour companies always protect their guests with full insurance coverage—not \r\n                            only for finances, but also for vehicles and travelers. With Madagascar Green Tours, \r\n                            you can book with confidence, knowing your trip is fully protected.          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"container content-section bg-light mb-4\">\r\n  <div class=\"card-styled\">\r\n    <div class=\"card-styled-body px-4 py-4\">\r\n      <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12\">\r\n          <h3 class=\"text-primary text-left font-inter-extra-bold fs-16\">\r\n          Our Travel Kit - Practical Information for Your Journey</h3>\r\n          <p class=\"text\">\r\n          To ensure our guests are well prepared, each booking includes a custom Madagascar travel kit. \r\n                            This guide contains essential information about the island, \r\n                            its people, and its culture. You\'ll also find:</p>\r\n          <ul class=\"font-inter-regular\">\r\n            <li>A practical packing list with recommended gear</li>\r\n            <li>Photography tips to capture Madagascar\'s unique wildlife and landscapes</li>\r\n            <li>A checklist for a basic first-aid kit</li>\r\n            <li>Useful Malagasy phrases to help you interact with locals</li>\r\n          </ul>\r\n          <p>In short, our travel kit is designed to give you \r\n                            everything you need for a smooth, enjoyable, and unforgettable \r\n                            journey in Madagascar.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"container content-section bg-light\">\r\n  <div class=\"card-styled\">\r\n    <div class=\"card-styled-body px-4 py-4\">\r\n      <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12\">\r\n          <h3 class=\"text-primary text-left font-inter-extra-bold fs-16\">\r\n          Conclusion</h3>\r\n          <p class=\"text\">From carefully selected Madagascar hotels and lodges, to adventurous camping tours, \r\n                            reliable vehicles, and full safety guarantees, Madagascar Green Tours ensures every detail \r\n                            of your trip is thoughtfully planned. With over two decades of experience as a trusted Madagascar \r\n                            tour operator, we provide travelers with authentic experiences, professional guidance, \r\n                            and lasting memories.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</section>', 'html', 'en', 1, 1, '2025-12-01 18:44:45', '2025-12-01 18:44:45'),
(87, 39, 'Content spanish', '<section id=\"about\" class=\"container content-section bg-light\" aria-labelledby=\"about-heading\">\r\n  <div class=\"card-styled\">\r\n    <div class=\"card-styled-body\">\r\n      <img src=\"/uploads/media/images/hotel-ranomafana.jpg\" class=\"float-image desktop-img\" alt=\"Ring-tailed lemur in Madagascar rainforest\" decoding=\"async\">\r\n        \r\n        <h1 class=\"text-center text-primary font-inter-extra-bold fs-20\">Información turística sobre Madagascar: hoteles, campings y excursiones</h1>\r\n      <h3 class=\"text-center font-inter-bold text-secondary fs-14\">\r\n        Conditions of sale for the tourist services      </h3>\r\n      <img src=\"/uploads/media/images/hotel-ranomafana.jpg\" class=\"float-image mobile-img\" alt=\"Ring-tailed lemur in Madagascar rainforest\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\">\r\n      <p>A la hora de planificar su viaje a Madagascar, una de las cuestiones más importantes es dónde se alojará. El turismo en Madagascar aún está en desarrollo, por lo que los hoteles de cinco estrellas al estilo europeo son poco frecuentes fuera de los principales centros turísticos. En la capital, Antananarivo, y en destinos populares como Nosy Be o Sainte Marie, los visitantes encontrarán una selección de cómodos hoteles y complejos turísticos de playa. Sin embargo, en muchas otras ciudades, los alojamientos son más sencillos y tradicionales.</p> <p>En Madagascar Green Tours, seleccionamos cuidadosamente hoteles, lodges y bungalós basándonos en más de 20 años de experiencia local. Dado que Madagascar no cuenta con un sistema oficial de clasificación de hoteles, evaluamos nosotros mismos los establecimientos, centrándonos en la limpieza, la comodidad, la calidad de las comidas y el servicio al cliente. La mayoría de los alojamientos son encantadores hoteles de gama media regentados por propietarios malgaches, a menudo construidos en armonía con la naturaleza y respetuosos con las comunidades locales. </p><p>En las zonas más remotas, los viajeros deben estar preparados para habitaciones básicas con servicios limitados, ya que los establecimientos de lujo son poco frecuentes fuera de las principales zonas turísticas. Si prefiere alojarse exclusivamente en lodges de lujo o hoteles boutique, por favor háganoslo saber con antelación. Los pocos resorts de lujo que hay en Madagascar tienen una gran demanda y suelen agotarse rápidamente. </p><img src=\"/uploads/media/images/shape-6.webp\" alt=\"shape-6\" style=\"position: absolute; bottom: 0; right: 0;\">\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section>\r\n  <div class=\"top_inside_divider\"></div>\r\n  <img src=\"/uploads/media/images/hotel-ranomafana-large.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; margin-top: -32px\" alt=\"shape-6\">\r\n\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"container mb-4\" style=\"margin-top: -90px\">\r\n  <div class=\"card-styled\">\r\n    <div class=\"card-styled-body px-4\">\r\n      <h3 class=\"text-center font-inter-extra-bold text-primary\">\r\n         Camping en Madagascar - Un Aventura Única Cerca de la Naturaleza      </h3>\r\n      <p>Porque nos especializamos en tours “off the beaten path,” algunos itinerarios incluyen experiencias de camping. \r\n                        Esta es la mejor manera de sumergirse en la naturaleza pura de Madagascar, \r\n                        lejos de las áreas turísticas congestionadas. Proporcionamos modernas tiendas livianas con excelente \r\n                        protección contra la lluvia (hasta 4000 mm de columna de agua), garantizando comodidad incluso durante las lluvias tropicales.</p>\r\n      <p>Los huéspedes generalmente duermen en tiendas individuales o dobles, con espacio extra para equipaje y equipo. \r\n                        Mientras se hospeda, nuestros cocineros profesionales preparan tres comidas frescas diarias, con especial atención \r\n                        a dietas vegetarianas y opciones aptas para alérgicos. Muchos viajeros dicen que la comida que se sirve en nuestros \r\n                        tours de camping es de lo mejor que disfrutan durante todo su viaje. Es una forma verdaderamente memorable \r\n                        de experimentar los paisajes y la naturaleza salvaje de Madagascar.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"container content-section bg-light\">\r\n  <div class=\"card-styled\">\r\n    <div class=\"card-styled-body\">\r\n      <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-lg-5 col-md-12 col-sm-12\">\r\n          <img src=\"/uploads/media/images/huyndai-h1.webp\" alt=\"car\" style=\"width:100%; border-radius: 10px\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"col-lg-7 col-md-12 col-sm-12\">\r\n          <h4 class=\"text-primary text-left font-inter-extra-bold fs-16\">\r\n          Vehículos - Transporte Seguro y Reliable en Madagascar</h4>\r\n          <p class=\"text text-justify\">\r\n            Viajar por Madagascar requiere un transporte confiable, ya que las distancias son largas y las condiciones de la carretera \r\n                            pueden ser desafiantes. Nuestros vehículos para tours de Madagascar incluyen 4x4 off-road cars, minibuses, \r\n                            y autobuses más grandes, dependiendo del tamaño del grupo. Cada vehículo cumple con estándares estrictos de seguridad, \r\n                            está completamente segurizado y conducido por conductores malagache experimentados.          </p>\r\n          <p>\r\n          Viajar por Madagascar requiere un transporte confiable, ya que las distancias son largas y las condiciones de la carretera \r\n                            pueden ser desafiantes. Nuestros vehículos para tours de Madagascar incluyen 4x4 off-road cars, minibuses, \r\n                            y autobuses más grandes, dependiendo del tamaño del grupo. Cada vehículo cumple con estándares estrictos de seguridad, \r\n                            está completamente segurizado y conducido por conductores ma