(50, 'INDRI INDRI TOUR', 'indri-indri-tour', 'en', 'tour_69271a0f17970', 'Indri Indri Tour Madagascar: Explore Unique Wildlife', 'Discover the Indri Indri Tour in Madagascar', 'If you have a few days left before you leave the capital, visiting Andasibe National Park is a good option. Here you can see the largestof lemur ; Indri Indri, and lemurs Island in Vakôna Forest (private reserve). The first day you visit a reptiles farm in pereyras . On day 2 and 3 you visit Andasibe National Park ( Analamazaotra or Mantadia ) and the last day you drive back to Antananarivo.', 'If you have a few days left before you leave the capital, visiting Andasibe National Park is a good option. Here you can see the largestof lemur ; Indri Indri, and lemurs Island in Vakôna Forest (private reserve). The first day you visit a reptiles farm in pereyras . On day 2 and 3 you visit Andasibe National Park ( Analamazaotra or Mantadia ) and the last day you drive back to Antananarivo.', 'Andasibe National Park (Analamazaotra/Périnet) – Andasibe National Park (Mantadia) – Antananarivo', 'tours/indri-indri-tour/indri.jpg', 'tours/indri-indri-tour/indri-indri.jpg', '[\"Encounter a unique wildlife experience in the national parks and private reserve\",\"Walk in the thorn forest to meet lemurs and endemic tropical birds.\",\"Authentic interaction with local people along your journey Sample Malagasy food while hiking in the Zafimaniry region water sport or relax on the Mozambique canal\",\"Overland journey from dry forest with baobabs to rainforest with exotic orchids.\"]', NULL, '[\"Airport transfers;\",\"Car, including fuel;\",\"Driver;\",\"Hotel during 3 nights;\",\"Park entrance fees;\",\"All taxes.\"]', '[\"Food and drinks;\",\"Local guide fees;\",\"Tips;\",\"Hotel before the tour starts and after the tour has ended;\",\"All other expenses\"]', NULL, NULL, 'easy', '', '', 'active', 1, 0, 'Indri Indri Tour Madagascar - Explore Unique Wildlife', 'Experience the Indri Indri tour Madagascar and explo