(66, 'TSIRIBIHINA ADVENTURE TOUR', 'tsiribihina-adventure-tour', 'en', 'tour_6927d1030a9a3', 'Experience the thrill of a Tsiribihina River adventure!', 'Experience the Thrill of Tsiribihina River Adventure', 'This tour offers you the chance to enjoy Madagascar\'s beautiful flora and fauna in a relaxed way. On the first day, your driver will pick you up at the airport and transfer you to your hotel in downtown Antananarivo. The next two days are spent driving to Antsirabe and Miandrivazo, where you\'ll board a dugout canoe for a three-day journey down the Tsiribihina River. Enjoy the scenery, wildlife, fishing boats, and villages along the way. You\'ll sleep in a tent by the river, where the boatmen and guides will provide delicious meals. At the end of the tour, you\'ll visit the famous Avenue des Baobabs near Morondava.', 'This tour offers you the chance to enjoy Madagascar\'s beautiful flora and fauna in a relaxed way. On the first day, your driver will pick you up at the airport and transfer you to your hotel in downtown Antananarivo. The next two days are spent driving to Antsirabe and Miandrivazo, where you\'ll board a dugout canoe for a three-day journey down the Tsiribihina River. Enjoy the scenery, wildlife, fishing boats, and villages along the way. You\'ll sleep in a tent by the river, where the boatmen and guides will provide delicious meals. At the end of the tour, you\'ll visit the famous Avenue des Baobabs near Morondava.', 'Antananarivo – Antsirabe – Miandrivazo – Tsiribihina rivier – Belo sur Tsiribihina – Tsingy de Bemaraha National Park – Avenue des Baobabs – Morondava', 'tours/tsiribihina-adventure-tour/tsingy.jpg', 'tours/tsiribihina-adventure-tour/baobab.webp', '[\"Find unique experience with untamed wildlife in National parks and private reserve\",\"Authentic interaction with local people throughout your journey on the river trips\",\"Overland journey from the river trips to tsingy de Bemaraha and alley of the baobabs with sunset\"]', NULL, '[\