ide,\",\"4WD from the riverside to Tsingy de Bemaraha NP, to Morondava\",\"Car ferry to Tsingy de Bemaraha NP and to Morondava\",\"Pirogue for 3 days,\",\"Boatman during the boat trip,\",\"Guide\\/cook assistance during the boat trip,\",\"Camping equipments: tent, mattresses and pillows,\",\"Meals and mineral water during the boat trip,\",\"Park entrace fees,\",\"All taxes.\"]', '[\"Food and drinks another days;\",\"Local guide fees;\",\"Tips;\",\"All other expenses\"]', NULL, NULL, 'easy', '', '', 'active', 0, 0, 'Tsiribihina River Relaxation Tour - Madagascar Green Tours', 'Experience ultimate Tsiribihina River relaxation on our tour!', 'tours madagascar, madagascar local tour company', 'template-tour', NULL, '2025-11-27 04:30:33', '2025-11-27 04:30:33'),
