(307, 68, 7, 'VISIT BETANIA', 'Today you visit the fisher village Betania by boat. After a picnic lunch near the village you return to Morondava.Overnight in hotel.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '2025-11-27 04:32:27', '2025-11-27 04:32:27'),
